I know how busy you guys can get.

33:00.813 --> 33:05.568
So, what's the topic of discussion?

33:05.652 --> 33:07.654
I've been hired by Meredith Powell

33:08.446 --> 33:11.282
to investigate the disappearance
of Paul Allen.

33:12.742 --> 33:15.411
