- Coffee?

33:21.084 --> 33:22.168
No, I'm okay.

33:22.251 --> 33:24.087
- Apollinaris?
- No, I'm okay.

33:26.089 --> 33:28.174
- Can you bring Mister...
- Kimball.

33:28.257 --> 33:29.509
Mr Kimball a bottle...

33:29.592 --> 33:32.011
- No, really, I'm okay.
- It's no problem.

33:34.806 --> 33:36.683
So, what's the topic of discussion?

33:36.766 --> 33:40.019
The disappearance of Paul Allen.

33:40.103 --> 33:41.270
Right.

33:41.354 --> 33:44.357
Well, I haven't...

33:44.941 --> 33:48.861
