34:11.342 --> 34:13.344
The American Gardens building,
West 81 st Street.

34:14.011 --> 34:16.556
- Nice. Very nice.
- Thanks.

34:17.181 --> 34:20.309
- What can you tell me about Paul Allen?
- I'm at a loss.

34:20.810 --> 34:22.562
He was part of that whole Yale thing.

34:22.645 --> 34:25.148
-"Yale thing"?
- Yeah, Yale thing.

34:25.231 --> 34:26.607
What do you mean, "Yale thing"?

34:26.690 --> 34:30.445
Well, I think for one that he was
probably a closet homosexual

34:30.527 --> 34:32.780
