35:00.725 --> 35:02.185
No, he just hung out there.

35:02.268 --> 35:04.312
And where did he go to school?

35:06.230 --> 35:09.484
- Don't you know this?
- I just wanted to know if you know.

35:13.362 --> 35:16.324
