Saint Paul's.

35:16.407 --> 35:19.994
Listen, I just... I just want to help.

35:21.621 --> 35:23.206
I understand.

35:25.750 --> 35:27.126
Do you have any witnesses or fingerprints?

35:27.210 --> 35:30.087
