36:02.411 --> 36:05.248
- So typical, isn't it?
- It's just strange.

36:05.498 --> 36:07.500
One day someone's walking around,

36:07.583 --> 36:10.294
going to work, alive, and then...

36:10.378 --> 36:11.796
Nothing.

36:12.797 --> 36:14.465
People just disappear.

36:15.258 --> 36:18.928
The earth just opens up
and swallows them.

36:19.762 --> 36:22.932
Eerie. Really eerie.

36:28.479 --> 36:30.773
